data.description: Move right in! This turn- key property is featuring 1,600 square feet, three bed rooms & two and a half bath rooms. Special features include vaulted ceilings, laminate vinyl plank flooring throughout the entire main level, fire place, floor to ceiling windows supplying tons of natural light, stainless steel kitchen appliances, second level laundry & much more! A combined kitchen & dining area open up to the sliding door leading right out to a private patio & yard space. The home also has a 2 car garage with the utility room conveniently located within. Upstairs all three bed rooms are generously sized & offer ample closet space. The primary bedroom has french doors, a huge walk in closet & an ensuite bathroom with large vanity, bath tub & shower shower combo. Close to I90 & just minutes to Randall Rd. for all shopping and entertainment. Move right into the wonderful Covington Lakes community today!
